    "Let E n be the many-body eigenenergies ordered as E n+1 > E n > E n-1 >..., then the nearest-neighbor level spacing is defined asδ n = E n+1 -E n.(27)The gap ratio isr n = min(δ n, δ n-1) max(δ n, δ n-1).",
